@startuml
title Sequence: Student Checks Course and Modules (Dashboard)

actor "Student" as S
participant "Frontend" as FE
participant "Backend (API)" as BE
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

note over S,FE
Precondition: Student is logged in (JWT stored).
end note

S -> FE: Open Dashboard
FE -> BE: GET /api/me/dashboard\nAuthorization: Bearer <JWT>

BE -> BE: Validate JWT + extract userId
BE -> BE: Authorize (student permissions)

BE -> DB: Load active course enrollment\n+ current/past module enrollments
DB --> BE: Course + Module enrollment rows
BE -> BE: Build StudentDashboardDto

BE --> FE: 200 OK\nStudentDashboardDto
FE --> S: Render course + module cards
@enduml
